    "description_long": "This is a rectangular yellow traffic sign mounted on a tall, slender metallic post. The front face of the sign displays bold black text reading 'Speed Bump Ahead', clearly intended to warn drivers of an upcoming road feature. The sign's surface appears smooth and slightly reflective, with the back showing some rust or weathering, indicating outdoor exposure. The post is cylindrical and metallic, likely galvanized steel, providing sturdy support for the sign. The sign is designed to be highly visible, with its bright color and clear lettering. This type of sign is commonly found in urban environments to alert motorists to slow down for speed bumps.",
